title: Real Eyes Realize Real Zeits 8/10: Big Ten, Secret Service, San Andreas, Derecho

description:
On this edition fo Real Zeits Jack and Miles discuss the Big Ten not holding any games this year, a Trump press conference in which he was rushed out of the room by Secret Service, there are more earthquakes along the San Andreas fault, and a particularly bad pattern of weather is hitting Chicago.
